{"tid":2516010,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"菲律賓外長向王毅致歉　讚揚王毅是外交偶像","createTime":"2021-05-04T11:07:31.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-04T11:18:05.000Z","uid":290118,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"23c92f9f9637d4f84cf58f906e08bfeadecedf6b","tid":2516010,"uid":290118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T11:07:31.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1589180-20210504.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1589180-20210504.htm&d=qHuNkoJYq05zO%2BFPSordK3psBjqOi2zFRj9KJcX5ApM%3D&h=d5d10d5d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1589180-20210504.htm&h=f8f6e5b6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1589180-20210504.htm</a><br />\n早前在社交網站發表附帶粗口言論，要求中方船隻離開菲中有主權爭議水域的菲律賓外長洛欽，先後向中國駐菲律賓大使，以及中國外長王毅致歉。<br />\n<br />\n洛欽在Twitter貼文，指若果王毅有使用Twitter，他對傷害對方感情深感抱歉，讚揚王毅是他的外交偶像，在思想和儀態上都優雅，自己難以模仿。<br />\n<br />\n菲律賓總統杜特爾特較早時強調，中國仍然是菲律賓的恩人，雖然兩國之間有衝突，但並不意味菲方要變得無禮，不尊重別人，菲律賓事實上亦有太多事要感謝中國。"},{"pid":"952ccd47d2adfd4345cc2d007c08c0c930b17723","tid":2516010,"uid":290118,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T11:07:43.000Z","msg":"垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55e4b29e0aab12bf9c91014588fd596c59c46d31","tid":2516010,"uid":151368,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T11:08:40.000Z","msg":"撚狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23f275117e7c4aa0389c52fb984a7a7d2c664a80","tid":2516010,"uid":155095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T11:10:30.000Z","msg":"撚中國，中國又吹唔漲 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://assets.post852.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/03184217/612.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fassets.post8